# Scalper_IBandRecentHL — User Guide

**Indicator:** `Scalper_IBandRecentHL`
**Type:** NinjaTrader 8 Indicator (overlay on price panel)
**Purpose:** Display Initial Balance (IB) and rolling Recent High/Low/Mid levels

