## Quick Reference Card

```
INSTALL:    Copy Scalper_IBandRecentHL.cs to
            Documents\NinjaTrader 8\bin\Custom\Indicators\
            Press F5 in NinjaScript Editor to compile.

ADD:        Right-click chart → Indicators → Scalper_IBandRecentHL → Add.

DEFAULTS:   IB Minutes = 60 (IB window length)
            Recent Minutes = 60 (rolling window)
            All Show* = true.

IB ANCHOR:  Always 9:30–10:30 NY Eastern Time, DST-safe.
            Locks at 10:30 ET. Persists until next 9:30 ET.

RECENT HL:  Always updating. Rolling N-minute window.

COLORS:     IB = green. Recent HL = blue.
            High/Low = thick line. Mid = thin line.

OUTPUT:     Watch NinjaScript Output for [IB] log messages
            confirming each reset and lock.

CSV:        This indicator does NOT write its own CSV.
            (The alerter strategy that uses these levels does.)
```

---

